bookorganizer.title: Book Organizer
bookorganizer.description: A Web-App for organizing your books into virtual bookshelves and sharing them via link or embed.

shelfrenderingengine.title: Shelf Rendering Engine
shelfrenderingengine.description: A highly flexible rendering engine for virtual shelves, inventories, and catalog-like UIs, designed for Vue.js and powered by strict TypeScript models.
